<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Anhui Congress Standing Committee Session Ends </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   OW3003143094 Hefei Anhui People's Radio Network in Mandarin 
1100 GMT 27 Feb 94 </F>

