<H3> <TI>   Further Reportage on Cross-Strait Talks </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Further Reportage on Cross-Strait Talks </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Official Issues Statement on Return </H4>

<F P=102> OW0304114994 Taipei Voice of Free China in English 0200 GMT 
2 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> OW0304114994 </F>
<F P=104>  Taipei Voice of Free China </F>
